[src:acts-of-union-1800/10-geo-4-p02] An Act for authorizing a Settlement of the Freehold and Copyhold Estates, late of Thomas Gregory Player Esquire, deceased, at Aldenham in the County of Hertford, under the Direction of the High Court of Chancery.
[src:acts-of-union-1800/10-geo-4-p02] An Act for naturalizing Ferdinand Stewart Campbell.
